{"tid":1733123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登們 以後唔好叫人死守啦","createTime":"2019-11-18T04:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T09:53:25.000Z","uid":98861,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5ab0e7b53fb7e8cdf96d3f24ffdd8577311c2e18","tid":1733123,"uid":98861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:47:13.000Z","msg":"咁耐以為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">贏</span>係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遊擊 突發</span><br />\n<br />\n今次轉左用<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">守城</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n暴大贏係因為地利<br />\n<br />\nPoly都叫人守 一個交通網絡既中間點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">守極都會無資源 無體力</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍師 帶風向既人 推post人<br />\n<br />\n諗清楚自己一舉一動會令到一件事既成敗<br />\n<br />\n大家都知唔應該送頭 就叫人坐以待斃<br />\n<br />\n我想知究竟係你係禁撚醒有方法守可以打贏呀<br />\n<br />\n定係你想害撚死手足<br />\n<br />\n你可以話呢個post 後馬後炮<br />\n<br />\n但係唔反省 係唔係要全滅 game over<br />\n<br />\n不可修補既情況出現 大家接受現實？<br />\n<br />\n希望大家清楚咩係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> be water to win</span>"},{"pid":"bdd2c1bda851313950d5b4b2181e3eac93d58025","tid":1733123,"uid":53440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:49:15.000Z","msg":"救左人先幫你推個POST <br />\n拉"},{"pid":"3f303f568c315f8515cb41c0a4a460f0ada8d708","tid":1733123,"uid":238695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9829d34f709005f4c696de330c6e4cc0bc86f0b6","tid":1733123,"uid":71428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:50:47.000Z","msg":"唔係唔守, 係守之前要諗下後路, 唔係一尾死守"},{"pid":"977fe1fd79aa3511043599248f6e245b85d47b94","tid":1733123,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:52:03.000Z","msg":"完全同意唔應該陣地<br />\n<br />\n檢討post - 打破政府一星期止暴制亂計畫<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1733073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1733073</a>"},{"pid":"51bc092fa9fa0a3ec3f52712084da0aa4d50e6dd","tid":1733123,"uid":293012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:53:28.000Z","msg":"叫你地走被你地屌係散水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/冷氣軍師/左膠：乜乜物物<br />\n呢個風氣真係要改，但講左成五個月啦，有冇變過呀？<br />\n<br />\n仲變本加厲添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3eefd1082b421984f9364c4d536ddb0cb8bd2b","tid":1733123,"uid":98861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"唔留後路 只係得兩口plan <br />\n<br />\n有後路 變化先會大"},{"pid":"d297fa8c51c5bace386ab6b47f31c3eabebeb54a","tid":1733123,"uid":98861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"664ce39557c0d5790797ab3a2a8751a881cfe46b","tid":1733123,"uid":167828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb711c746596fb3e992108419ea4d12a84535a69","tid":1733123,"uid":293012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"664ce39557c0d5790797ab3a2a8751a881cfe46b","tid":1733123,"uid":167828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51bc092fa9fa0a3ec3f52712084da0aa4d50e6dd","tid":1733123,"uid":293012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:53:28.000Z","msg":"叫你地走被你地屌係散水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/冷氣軍師/左膠：乜乜物物<br />\n呢個風氣真係要改，但講左成五個月啦，有冇變過呀？<br />\n<br />\n仲變本加厲添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"話唔定呢啲先係真五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話我分化撚都係咁講<br />\n<br />\n  //事前屌，就罵你散水撚。<br />\n爆緊鑊時席，就叫你解決咗問題先屌。<br />\n事後屌，都過咗去，鬧嚟做乜，馬後砲私怨撚。<br />\n<br />\n任何時候都唔屌得，你永遠不會反省。<br />\n中大一役走到是好彩，幾天後就去理大。<br />\n今次畀佢哋走得甩，下次又不知去邊。//"},{"pid":"736f794ba2cceb7b3b3d2c15dc4959058a371efa","tid":1733123,"uid":281763,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:57:01.000Z","msg":"暴大嬴實不因地利，地利只讓佢地難攻不會讓佢地放棄圍城(你畫面都見到原沙田已一排狗車入緊去) <br />\n暴大後面有好多人同高官周旋，幾多人用盡自己人脈去幫，前任/現任校長十萬通電話咁打&hellip;<br />\n當然佢地只敢暗地傾，一浮面就得罪好多人<br />\n而poly無有地位嘅人咁熱心幫&hellip;"},{"pid":"4f6649a47e36b6af0472748a9d357ab4c457c2a7","tid":1733123,"uid":98861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8792f07491709b64c931e50923109cfc85a71e74","tid":1733123,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:53:25.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過連登係人都上得黎"}]}